translations.A Calendar app for Nextcloud. Easily syn:
A Calendar app for Nextcloud. Easily sync events from various devices with your Nextcloud and edit them online.

* üöÄ **Integration with other Nextcloud apps!** Like Contacts, Talk, Tasks, Deck and Circles
* üåê **WebCal Support!** Want to see your favorite team's matchdays in your calendar? No problem!
* üôã **Attendees!** Invite people to your events
* ‚åö **Free/Busy!** See when your attendees are available to meet
* ‚è∞ **Reminders!** Get alarms for events inside your browser and via email
* üîç **Search!** Find your events at ease
* ‚òëÔ∏è **Tasks!** See tasks or Deck cards with a due date directly in the calendar
* üîà **Talk rooms!** Create an associated Talk room when booking a meeting with just one click
* üìÜ **Appointment booking** Send people a link so they can book an appointment with you [using this app](https://apps.nextcloud.com/apps/appointments)
* üìé **Attachments!** Add, upload and view event attachments
* üôà **We‚Äôre not reinventing the wheel!** Based on the great [c-dav library](https://github.com/nextcloud/cdav-library), [ical.js](https://github.com/mozilla-comm/ical.js) and [fullcalendar](https://github.com/fullcalendar/fullcalendar) libraries.
